438
00:34:02,680 --> 00:34:08,530
Zhromaždite sa okolo.
Pre náš krásny let, fighting!

439
00:34:54,880 --> 00:34:56,060
Áno, učiteľ.

440
00:34:57,450 --> 00:34:59,420
Sme...ďalší na rade.

441
